
### `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# C extensions
*.so

# Packages
venv/
*.egg
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
eggs/
parts/
var/
sdist/
wheels/
*.pip
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt

# Flask specific files
instance/
.env

# Pytest and coverage reports
.cache/
.coverage
coverage.xml
*.cover
.hypothesis/
pytestdebug.log

# PyCharm and IDE specific files
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Other backups
*.bak
*.backup
